  "remarks": "JSC “DUKS” is the main producer of rocket missiles, including AA-11 “Archer” which are carried by Russian SU-27 fighter jets and are used by Russia in its war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC “DUKS” has received an appreciation from the President of\nthe Russian Federation, Vladimir Putin, for its great contribution to the creation of aviation technology and strengthening the country’s defense capability. JSC “DUKS” partners are the Russian Ministry of Defense and Rosoboronexport (Russian Defense Export).",
